                  "htmlContent": "<div class=\"dangerous-good-intro\">\n<h2 class=\"context-h1\">Items allowed and prohibited in your luggage</h2>\n<p class=\"intro\">Restricted items may endanger the health and safety of people, the environment, or aircraft.</p>\n</div>",
